This directory contains files for adapting libmarpa to
Win32.  The Win32 developer should note that testing on Win32 is
*NOT* part of the test regime of libmarpa.
These files are upstreamed to the libmarpa repo
by Win32 users, and passed on in the hope that they will
be useful.
When changes
are make to libmarpa, no tests are made to check if those
changes break the install procedure suggested by these files.
Nonetheless, it is hoped that the files in this directory will
be better than nothing.
